cText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1003031, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, bless Muhammad and the Household of Muhammad and hasten their Relief. I have recited what You have decreed from Your Book, that which You sent down to Your Prophet, the Truthful One. May Allah’s blessings be on him and his family. So to You belongs all praises my Lord. O Allah, make me from among those who Enforce its obligations, and disallow its forbidden acts, Believe in its clear and its ambiguous verses. And make it a companion for me in my grave, and a companion in my rising, And make me among those who rise, for every verse recited, a rank of the most elevated aameen, Lord of the Worlds.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Rehmat farma Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur unki Aal (a.s) par aur unke zuhoor mein taajil (jaldi) farma. Ay Ma’bood! Mai ne Teri kitaab (Qur’an) mein se itna padha jitna Tu ne chaha, keh jise Tu ne naazil farmaya apne sachche Nabi (s.a.w.a) par, pas hamd Tere hi liye hai, ay hamare Rabb. Ay Ma’bood! Mujhe un logo’n mein rakh jinho ne Qur’an ke halaal ko halaal aur haraam ko haraam jaana aur uski mustaqil aur zumani aayato’n par imaan laaye aur Qur’an ko meri qabr ka ham-dam aur mere hashr ka saathi bana de aur mujhe un logo’n mein rakh keh jo har aayat ke padhne se ek ek darja buland hote jaate hai, buland-tar Jannat mein aisa ho, ay jahano ke Rabb.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! محمدؐ وآل محمدؑ پر رحمت نازل فرما اور ان کے آخرکے ظہور میں تعجیل فرما۔ اے معبود! میں نے تیری کتاب میں سے اتنا پڑھا جتنا تو نے چاہا کہ جسے تو نے نازل فرمایا اپنے سچے نبیؐ پر، پس حمد تیرے ہی لیے ہے اے ہمارے رب اے معبود! مجھے ان لوگوں میں رکھ جنہوں نے قرآن کے حلال کو حلال اور حرام کو حرام گردانا اور اس کی مستقل اور ذومعنی آیتوں پر ایمان لائے اور قرآن کو میری قبر کا ہم دم اور میرے حشر کاساتھی بنا دے اور مجھے ان لوگوں میں رکھ کہ جو ہر آیت کے پڑھنے سے ایک ایک درجہ بلند ہوتے جاتے ہیں بلندتر جنت میں ایساہو اے جہانوں کے رب۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE MOHAMMADIN WA A’J-JIL FARAJA-HUM. ALLAAHUMMA INNEE QAD QARA-ATO MAA QA-ZAIY-TA MIN KETAABE-KAL LAZEE AN-ZAL-TAHU A’LAA NABIYYE-KAS SADEQE SALLAL-LAAHO A’LAIY-HE WA AALE-HI, FA-LAKAL HAMDO RABBA-NAA. ALLAAHUMAM-MAJ A’L-NEE MIM-MAN YO-HILLO HALAA-LAHU WA YO-HARRE-MO HARAAMA-HU WA YOA-MENO BE-MOHKA-MEHI WA MOTA-SHAABE-HEHI WAJ-A’L-HO OON-SAN FEE QABREE WA OON-SAN FEE HASH-REE WAJ-A’L-NEE MIM-MAN TUR-QAIY-HE BE-KULLE AAYA-TIN QARA-AHAA DARAJA-TAN FEE A’LAA I’LLIYYINA AAMEENA RABBAL A’A-LAMEEN.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَعَجِّلْ فَرَجَهُمْ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّیْ قَدْ قَرَاَتُ مَا قَضَیْتَ مِنْ كِتَابِكَ الَّذِیْ اَنْزَلْتَهٗ عَلٰی نَبِیِّكَ الصَّدِقِ صَلَّ اللهُ عَلَیْهِ وَ آلِهٖ، فَلَكَ الْحَمْدُ رَبَّنَا۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ اجْعَلْنِیْ مِمَّنْ یُحِلُّ حَلَالَهٗ وَ یُحَرِّمُ حَرَامَهٗ وَیُؤْمِنُ بِمُحْكَمِهٖ وَمُتَشَابِهِهٖ وَاجْعَلْهُ اُنْسًا فِیْ قَبْرِیْ وَاُنْسًا فِیْ حَشْرِیْ وَاجْعَلْنِیْ مِمَّنْ تُرْقَیْهِ بِكُلِّ آیَۃٍ قَرَاَهَا دَرَجَۃً فِیْ اَعْلٰی عِلِّیِّیْنَ آمِیْنَ رَبَّ الْعَالَمِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicTe